    "body": "Thanks! These changes sound reasonable, but practically it's not easy to make changes to the DOM with our current setup. Have you considered using a connector? seems like for #6618, #6619 as well those are all about pagination widget so likely could all be solved with a single custom widget.\n\nIf you'd be interested in contributing, it could be an option to convert the pagination widget to one that uses the same rendering along all flavours in the `next` branch, and then fix these issues. Let me know if you have bandwidth for that",
